Dragons' Den Ireland - Series 6, Episode 3




A new batch of entrepreneurs hope to impress Barry O'Sullivan, Gavin Duffy, Ramona Nicholas, Peter Casey and Eamonn Quinn, including Dubliner Brendan O'Neill, who has big plans for a customised clothing business. Meanwhile, inventor Barry Sheehan believes his device solves an everyday problem and a duo pitch their premium range of sports supplements.
